INKANTOLO yesiFunda eRustenburg, imgwebe udilikajele owesilisa yambansela ngeminyaka engu-15 ngaphezulu ngamacala okubulala. Ngesikhathi kuqulwa icala, inkantolo yezwa ngendlela uMnuz George Motsamai Ntlheng (48), abulala ngayo umkakhe oyengasahlali naye uNksz Boitumelo Daphney Molabatsi (36), nomngani wakhe uNksz Emelda Matsho (38), eSunrise Park ngo-2019. Kuthiwa ngoMashi 4, 2019 uNtlheng walandela umkakhe eyongena emzini womngani wakhe. Kuthe uNksz Molabatsi esalinde umngani wakhe kulo muzi, wahlaselwa ngumyeni wakhe wamgwaza ngommese, ephindelela. Umsolwa washiya umufi lapho waqonda emzini wesoka lomkhake. Isoka lakwazi ukubaleka, kwathi kusenjalo kwaqhamuka umngani kamufi, wazithela kuNtlheng. “Lo mlisa wahlasela umngani wambhokoda ngommese naye,” kusho amaphoyisa. Amalungu omphakathi abikela amaphoyisa ngalesi sehlakalo. Amaphoyisa aseBoitekong, amthungatha umsolwa amthola ngabo ubusuku besigameko.